acceptance_criteria:
- Middleware matcher gates POST/PUT/PATCH/DELETE and /api/private|/api/secure routes;
- Shared requireSession helper returns 401 when missing session and reused across handlers/actions;
- Public read APIs set Vary: Cookie with cache-control separation;
- Tests cover anon vs authed requests and caching headers;
- Docs updated and feature flagged if needed.

- Introduce Turnstile or hCaptcha token verification service-side;
- Gate high-risk writes (comments/votes/first write) when anon or IP flagged;
- Rate-limit + log captcha failures;
- Tests cover pass/fail paths and bypass for trusted users;
- Feature can be toggled via env.

- Light/dark semantic tokens (surface/overlay/brand/info/success/warn/danger, data-viz);
- Motion tokens (distance-based durations/easing);
- Lint rule rejecting raw hex;
- Theme provider + token docs page;
- Storybook/MDX playground for tokens/primitives.

- Sparkline/bar/radial components;
- Data-viz tokens;
- Empty/error states;
- Docs and stories;
- Light/dark parity.

- Voice/tone guide;
- Microcopy library;
- Glossary;
- Empty/zero-state templates;
- Docs published in design system.

- Contrast/focus/ARIA audit fixes;
- Keyboard paths verified for nav/search/builder;
- Perf budgets per route with LCP/CLS monitors;
- Skeleton/suspense usage aligned to budgets.

- Playwright visual baselines per breakpoint;
- Interaction smoke tests;
- DESIGN_SYSTEM update;
- Adoption playbook + migration guide;
- Changelog + in-product 'What’s new'.

- Rebuild primitives (Button, IconButton, Input, Select, Textarea, Checkbox/Radio, Tooltip, Badge/Pill, Card, Tag/Chips, Tabs, Pagination, Breadcrumbs, Modal/Sheet, Toast, Stepper, Command Palette, Search field);
- Utility classes for text/grid/elevation/focus;
- Storybook stories per primitive with light/dark snaps;
- No hex lint violations;
- A11y roles/labels in stories.

- Desktop nav/footer refreshed to new tokens;
- Mobile nav/search sheet with quick filters;
- Command palette entry points added;
